00:32:43.610 --> 00:32:47.810
So let me do it in two stages.

00:32:47.810 --> 00:32:51.030
Here are the numbers.

00:32:51.030 --> 00:32:57.390
And here is 5 4, 3, 2, 1, 0.

00:32:57.390 --> 00:33:04.010
Possibly minus 1, minus
