state in the Hilbert space,

00:58:05.170 --> 00:58:07.580
you plug it in here.

00:58:07.580 --> 00:58:11.150
And by acting with
this unitary operator,

00:58:11.150 --> 00:58:13.230
you get the state
at the later time.

00:58:16.360 --> 00:58:22.550
